                <h1 class="nhsuk-u-margin-bottom-5">Error summary</h1>
                <p class="nhsuk-body-l">Use this component at the top of a page to summarise any errors a user has made.</p>
                <p class="nhsuk-u-margin-bottom-8">When a user makes an error, you must show both an error summary and an <a href="/patterns/error-message">error message</a> next to each answer that contains an error.</p>
